01b[C details here: https://suppo\u001b[Ct.cl\u001b[Cude.com/en/articles/15424964-claude-fable-5-promotional-access\u001b[13;2H\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;239m\u001b[48;5;237m\u276f \u001b[38;5;231mAdd one short joke about credentials to jokes.md, then commit it, push it, and open a pull request. This is issue #206.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[16;1H\u001b[49m\u001b[38;5;231m\u25cf\u001b[39m I'll start by looking at the repo and the existing jokes.md.\u001b[K\u001b[18;1H \u001b[C\u001b[38;5;246mRan \u001b[1m2\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[38;5;246m shell commands \u001b[39m\u001b[C\u001b[K\u001b[20;1H\u001b[38;5;231m\u25cf\u001b[C\u001b[39mjokes.md doesn't exist\u001b[Cyet,\u001b[Cso\u001b[CI'll\u001b[Ccreate\u001b[Cit.\u001b[CLet\u001b[Cme\u001b[Ccheck\u001b[Cwith\u001b[Cthe\u001b[Cadvisor\u001b[Cfirst,\u001b[Cand\u001b[Cdeclare\u001b[Cthe\u001b[Cissue\u001b[Csince\u001b[CGitHub\u001b[Cwrites\u001b[Care\u001b[Cgated.\u001b[22;1H\u001b[38;5;114m\u25cf\u001b[C\u001b[39m\u001b[1mAdvising\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[38;5;246m using Opus 4.8\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;246m  \u23bf \u00a0\u2714 Advisor has reviewed the conversation and will apply the feedback \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;246m\u25cf\u001b[39m \u001b[1mWrite\u001b[m\u000f(jokes.md)\u001b[K\u001b[27;3H\u001b[38;5;216mDiscombobu\u001b[3Cing\u2026\u001b[30;3H\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[H\u001b[38;5;174m\u2502\u001b[15C\u001b[38;5;246m/tmp/rein-demo-m6ozjlj5\u001b[14C\u001b[38;5;174m\u001b[2m\u2502\u001b[105C\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[38;5;174m\u2502\u001b[27;32H\u001b[38;5;246m6\u001b[30;3H\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[H\u001b[K\r\n \u001b[38;5;174m\u258e\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;174mExtended through July 19\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[3;2H\u001b[38;5;174m\u258e\u001b[C\u001b[39mWe're\u001b[Cextending\u001b[CClaude\u001b[CFable\u001b[C5\u001b[Caccess\u001b[Con\u001b[Call\u001b[Cpaid\u001b[Cplans,\u001b[Cas\u001b[Cwell\u001b[Cas\u001b[Ckeeping\u001b[CClaude\u001b[CCode\u2019s\u001b[Cweekly\u001b[Crate\u001b[Climits\u001